口試委員-江哲銘
口試委員-謝育穎
指導教授-賴榮平



關鍵字(中)
文化設施規劃社區博物館地方文化館


關鍵字(英)
Local Cultural MuseumCommunity MuseumPlanning for Cultural institutions


學科別分類



中文摘要
「地方文化館」作為一個鄉鎮或社區的文化據點，對外展現地方特色之場所。其功能除典藏保存、展示文物功能外，另一方面也讓居民擁有較多參與文化活動的機會，以提升全民文化參與、創造與分享文化資源、均衡城鄉發展。希望能將文化結合社區特色並激發地方居民主動參與之動力。然而，從2001年第一期地方文化館計劃開始至今，因部份地方文化館閒置或營運不佳，導致地方文化館受人的質疑，被諷稱「蚊子館」。藉由文建會(2007)，針對全國924所展演設施進行調查，現況為「不正常開放」的設施，其中72％為鄉鎮型(即相當於地方文化館層級)文化展演設施。因此，本研究以臺南縣市地區地方文化館為調查對象。利用文獻回顧法蒐集影響地方文化館存活之相關因素，並建立調查項目架構，而後進行館舍現況調查，藉由邏輯斯迴歸分析出影響地方文化館存活最為明顯相關者。本研究主要結論如下：一、臺南縣市地方文化館使用現況：臺南縣與臺南市半數以上地方文化館共同特性：(一)外部因素部分1.交通便利性：66％之館舍皆提供16部以上之停車位，停車便利性良好。(二)內部因素部分1. 建築物空間概況：59％館舍建築物為新建。2. 組織層級：56％館舍設置單位為法人團體。3. 人力資源：66％館舍無社區團體參與。4. 財務狀況：88％館舍為免收門票費、67％館舍主要營運收入來源為隸屬單位核付預算。臺南縣與臺南市地方文化館差異特性：1. 當地人口密度：臺南市8成館舍位於人口密度4000人/k㎡以上地區，臺南縣8成館舍位於人口密度1000人/k㎡以下地區。2. 公共交通可性：臺南市館舍公共交通便利程度優於臺南縣館舍。3. 景觀旅遊資源豐富性：臺南市館舍周圍景點數量多於臺南縣館舍。4. 營運輔導單位：臺南市7成館舍營運並無其他輔導單位，臺南縣5成館舍有公立單位輔導的情形。二、分析影響地方文化館存活之相關因素：本研究針對27個因素變項進行與「地方文化館開放情形」相關分析，發現臺南縣市地方文化館之使用建築物情形、設置單位組織、經營單位組織、展示內容主題類型、宣傳多樣性等五項，與館舍是否正常開放情形有明顯相關性。


英文摘要
A public cultural institution like a local cultural museum or community museum is where the local culture can be displayed.  Besides preserving and exhibiting the objects, the other important aim of this type of museum is to get the community involved with cultural activities so as to balance the diverse development between the urban and the rural areas.  	However, since year 2001 the Local Cultural Museums Project I was launched, local cultural museum in some area have been criticized and mocked as “museums for mosquitoes” for failing in regular opening or remaining unvisited. According to the survey of all of the cultural institutions in Taiwan that was executed by the Council for Cultural Affairs, 72% of those institutions that do not open regularly belong to villages and towns that refer to local cultural institutions.	This research chiefly focuses on the local cultural museums in both Tainan Area. It is conducted firstly by literature review to sort out the relevant factors to the operation of local cultural museums, and secondly by Logistic Regression to unravel the most influential features that keep local cultural museums working effectively. The conclusions of this research are as follows.  	Present situation of local cultural museums in Tainan AreaA.	The Common Features among over half of the local cultural museums in Tainan City and County Areaa.	External Feature:1.	Transportation Efficiency: 66% of the research targets provide parking lot that contains at least 16 parking spaces.  This shows good transportation efficiency.b.	Internal Feature: 1.	Building Types: 59% of them are newly built for local cultural museums. 2.	Organizational Level: 56% of the research cases are run by corporations.3.	Human resources: 66% of the research cases do not get the community involved.4.	Financial Status: Over 88% of the research cases are ticket-free; 66% of them rely on the government subsidy.  B.	The different features between local cultural museums in Tainan City and County Area1.	 Population density: 80% of the museums in Tainan City locate in the spot where  the population density is measured beyond 4,000people/k㎡ ;  80% of the museums in Tainan County locate in the spot where it is measured below 1,000people/k㎡. 2.	Transportation efficiency: The museums in Tainan City are more accessible than those in Tainan County in terms of transportation efficiency.3.	Tourist Spot Abundance: Museums in Tainan City are more adjacent to the tourist spots in the neighborhood than in Tainan County.4.	Counseling institution: 70% of the museums in Tainan City are not assisted by any counseling institution; 50% of those in Tainan County do obtain the assistance offered by public institution. 	Features that affect the operation of local cultural museumsThis research selects and aims at 27 features to analyze their relevance to the possibility of regular opening of local cultural museums.  As a result, it discovers that building types, founding organization, operational organization, display topic and type, promoting variety are five essential features that allow those local cultural museums in both Tainan City and County to open to the public regularly.


