      第 17 筆 ---------------------------------------------------------------------




系統識別號
U0026-0812200915301761


論文名稱(中文) 
      
組織變革、領導型態、組織文化與工作績效之研究-以台灣南部三所大學為例


論文名稱(英文) 
      
The Relationship between the Organizational Chang,Leadership Style, Organizational Culture and Job Performance- Evidence from Three Universities in Southern Taiwan.


校院名稱
成功大學


系所名稱(中)
企業管理學系專班


系所名稱(英)
Department of Business Administration (on the job class)


學年度
97


學期
2


出版年
98


研究生(中文)
黃瓈慧


學號
r4796104


學位類別
碩士


語文別
中文


口試日期
2009-07-25


論文頁數
86頁


口試委員
口試委員-陳淑惠
指導教授-張淑昭
口試委員-許永明



關鍵字(中)
工作績效領導型態組織文化組織變革


關鍵字(英)
Leadership StyleOrganizational ChangeJob PerformanceOrganizational Culture


學科別分類



中文摘要
本研究目的在探討學校組織因應環境變遷，採取組織變革的策略，對於組織文化、領導型態與員工工作績效所造成的影響，進而探討其間之關聯性。本研究採用群集抽樣問捲調查方式，以南部地區三所私立大專院校教職員為研究對象，發放250份問捲，回收212份，回收率84.8%，以SPSS統計軟體進行實證資料分析。研究結果顯示組織變革對於組織文化有顯著影響，尤其以組織結構變革對於組織文化的影響最為顯著；但是，組織變革對於領導型態的影響，僅有組織結構變革具有顯著影響；組織文化對於工作績效的影響來看，僅以共識型、發展型有顯著影響，尤其以共識型的組織文化對於工作績效最有顯著的影響。領導型態對於工作績效的影響來看，魅力感化、精神激勵、智力啟發與個別關懷皆有顯著影響，尤其以魅力感化最為顯著；組織變革對於工作績效的影響來看，各構面因素都有顯著影響，尤其以組織結構變革對於員工的工作績效而言最為顯著，此研究結果可提供給組織做為制定組織變革策略之參考。


英文摘要
The purpose of this study is to discuss the effect and relationship between “Organizational Culture”, “Leadership style” and “Personal effectiveness” due to “Organizational change” responding to the environment change. Employees in three universities in southern Taiwan are used as examples for group sampling analysis. There were 250 questionnaires sent out, 212 were gotten back in the end with 84.4% of rate of recovery. The study uses SPSS to carry out proper statistical analysis.The result shows that there are some effects of organizational culture due to the organizational change, structure change especially. About the leadership style, only structure change may result in the change of leadership style. “Clan” and “Adhocracy” organizational culture may result in different personal effectiveness, “Clan” especially. “Charisma or idealized influenced”, “Inspirational motivation”, “Intellectual stimulation” and “Individualized consideration” leadership style may result in different job performance, “Charisma or idealized influenced” especially. Otherwise, the data analysis reveals organizational change may affect job performance, structure change especially. These results could be under consideration while developing the strategy of organizational change.


